This is Skyline OMS (Order Management System)

Stack:
Laravel 12
React + Inertia
TailwindCSS
MySQL

Architecture:
Follow docs/SYSTEM_ARCHITECTURE.md

Business rules:
Follow docs/BUSINESS_RULES.md

Coding style:
Follow docs/CODING_STANDARDS.md

Modules:
Follow docs/MODULES.md

UI Guidlines:
Follow docs/UI_GUIDELINES.md

Never generate code that violates the business rules.

Always:
- create migrations for database changes
- create services for business logic
- keep controllers thin
- use form requests for validation